e\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_27054032\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 02, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qce1767361237143.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qce1767361237143.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qce1767361237143.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qce1767361237143\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The following process explains how the Layout Mode Property controls layout generation\n\t\tfrom definition to runtime.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qce1767361237143__section_ol4_mz3_vhc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729162e49\">Main DSP Processing</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">When processing a DSP, the Layout Mode determines how the final HTML is\n\t\t\t\tconstructed:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qce1767361237143__ul_cp1_c1j_vhc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Generated:</strong><p class=\"p\">Layout template provides complete HTML with component\n\t\t\t\t\t\tbinding points</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Fragment:</strong><p class=\"p\">DSP Layout fragment is wrapped within layout template\n\t\t\t\t\t\tstructure</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Full Document:</strong><p class=\"p\">DSP Layout is sent to the browser without\n\t\t\t\t\t\tmodification</p></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qce1767361237143__section_qqd_qfj_vhc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d729162e79\">Contained DSP Processing</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">For contained DSPs (DSPs called from within other DSPs), the processing differs:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qce1767361237143__ul_lb5_rfj_vhc\">\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Generated:</strong><p class=\"p\">Component widgets render within provided structure</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Fragment:</strong><p class=\"p\">DSP Layout fragment becomes part of the response\n\t\t\t\t\tcontent</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Full Document:</strong><p class=\"p\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;head&gt;</code> section is removed and\n\t\t\t\t\t\tonly body content is used</p></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_27054032\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_27054032\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Processing Flow Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 02, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The following process explains how the Layout Mode Property controls layout generation from definition to runtime. Main DSP Processing When processing a DSP, the Layout Mode determines how the final HTML is constructed: Generated: Layout template provides complete HTML with component binding points Fragment: DSP Layout fragment is wrapped within layout template structure Full Document: DSP Layout is sent to the browser without modification Contained DSP Processing For contained DSPs (DSPs called from within other DSPs), the processing differs: Generated: Component widgets render within provided structure Fragment: DSP Layout fragment becomes part of the response content Full Document: The <head> section is removed and only body content is used Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}